2.00	Hasilpur	Hasilpur	Hasilpur (Urdu: ) is a city in Bahawalpur District in east central Punjab, Pakistan. The city is located between the Satluj River and the Indian border and lies 96 km east of the district capital Bahawalpur. The city is also the headquarters of Hasilpur Tehsil an administrative subdivision of the district the city itself is divided into to two parts, "Old Hasilpur" and "Hasilpur Mandi". Hasilpur is situated at the brink of Cholistan.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bb/VehariRoad.jpg/300px-VehariRoad.jpg
